author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl points towards the woman "So, you thought that you could evade me, Voreverl Leocot, by hiding in such an open area!? Gwehahah! What a foolish plan! Luckily for you, I'm willing to have a discussion, rather than sicking my minions on you immediately!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
She turns around. "Intu?-oh. Hm. Voreverl, yeah? Alright." She stands up and walks over, raising an eyebrow at Blanche.

"I am Neko, the people’s revolutionnaire from the city of frozen air. Pleased to make your acquaintance." She extends a hand.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl accepts the handshake, cautiously "More revolutionaries, huh? Ugh, I'm getting kind of sick of them, to be honest. But I do have reason to believe you'll make an acceptable ally."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She giggles. "You're an unusual one. You approach me with such boldness and aplomb. I can appreciate that. Intuition has the same kind of charm. Would you like to converse somewhere warmer?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Trying to get the upper hand in the conversation, are you? Think I'll be off my game just because we move to your desired location? Gwehah! Think again! My intimidation doubles when I'm not freezing! Where did you have in mind, then?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "The tower. I live there." She begins walking.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Hello, Furn, by the way. Good to see you well."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Furn mutters incoherently.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Such a predictable location, but a lair that towers over the people *is* a good way to induce fear in them..." Voreverl follows Neko.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
They arrive at the same building as before. "You can leave, Skelt. I just wanted to do some reminiscing. Thank you very much."

Skelt stammers. "Uh, you're w--well, it's, y-know, no problem, uh. You too." Then he leaves.

The first floor of this building is sparse, but Neko walks up to the second floor lounge.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl keeps following Neko yeah "So, how'd you come to control this place? It already exist and you staged a violent takeover? Or did you embezzle some funds to build it? It's a pretty nice lair, all things considered. Wouldn't mind having a place like this to work out some schemes in."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She takes a seat. "It was already property I practically owned. When I ended up settling down in here it was a natural choice. I just had to make it livable. It has served my activity well."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Right, right, activities..." Voreverl stares off for a second "Gweheheh, well, let's jump into the reason I came. I'm looking for travel to the capital, but more than that, I've heard that you're a successful influencer! Currently, my goal is to be feared as a force of pure evil by this whole world! So, uh, any advice on that would be helpful. Not that I need it."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Pure evil? Why would you want that, exactly? It's a bit strange to hear."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Because I *am* pure evil, duh. I just arrived here, and it's really frustrating how no one knows about me yet! So I need to get the word out!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Interesting. I think that itself will get the word out. This world incentivizes being crazy. Those who wield power are the most deluded." Neko smiles. "I intend to be an extremist for moderation; to attempt to work within this system to prevent disorder and irrationality. I suppose this puts us at ideological odds."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: She laughs. "That's no reason to be inhospitable, though! Would you like anything to drink?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Fetch me whatever soda you have on hand, I'm not picky. The environmental impact of their production represents my evil perfectly fine."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Voreverl is handed a Dr Bebber.

"Pardon my rudeness, but you don't seem local. How exactly did you find yourself on my doorstep?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl takes a long swig of the drink and then motions to Furn "I was told of this place by my minion. He suggested it as our next stop on my path to infamy. Judging by your 'ideology' though, I'm starting to think his head could do to be bolted on a bit tighter."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Neko takes a deep breath. "That's not what I meant. By *not local*, I mean *not of this world*. Am I correct?" All traces of humor are gone from her expression.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Ugh, sooner or later I'll be able to drop that as a fun reveal. Yes, yes, I'm from another world, whatever. As far as how, I really don't understand the mechanics of it yet. I black out, show up here, and vice versa. Even if I did understand it, I'd keep that close to my chest for my next evil scheme."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Her eyes light up. "Earth, right?!"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Yeah, that's right. Could you tone it down a bit? Kind of pitiable seeing someone so excited over such a boring place."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Oh, it's true what they say about the grass being greener... the very idea of someone being *bored* with such a place!" 
She stands up and paces around. "I mean, you've got the greats -- Socrates, Barack Obama, Ke$ha! It's a veritable paradise. And electricity!" She stares at you. "It's true, right? The heart can be restarted, right?!"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl has a mixed look of confusion and amusement "Uh... Yeah, that's- that's a thing, but... really? That's what excites you? You live in a world where magic exists, and you give a shit about medical technology? Ugh, I can't believe I ended up meeting with a nerd."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She scoffs. "Magic is nonsense. It can be used to conduct electricity, I guess. That's a plus." Neko causes the lights to flicker in the house with her hands doing the palpatine thing.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Okay, sure, whatever. Look, I didn't come to debate the value of Earth. I would try to forget about that place entirely if I didn't know that... Uh, nevermind, look, whatever you think is interesting about it is clearly just a misunderstanding. It's not like electronics don't exist here too."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Well, yeah. I've managed to acquire some items from Earth using my connections. Intuition *loves* that gun, haha."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, at least your taste in Earth's inventions aren't *entirely* unreasonable. I'll give them this, they are great at creating weapons of war! Maybe I'll learn how to create nuclear bomb here, that's sure to make the people fear me!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “No, it won’t come to that. By the time you manage, I will be in a position to stop you. Actually… hm.” She stares at Furn.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Oh, you think too little of me, obviously I wouldn't *use* it. No, no, what makes people afraid is just the idea! Only an idiot would actually kill their subjects, that's less people to be aware of my evil!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “A deterrent is more reasonable, yes. To be honest, though, I’m uncertain on whether nuclear weaponry would even work here. The levels on which our world differs from yours run quite deep.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “Though if the psychological aspect is what you are seeking, that does not matter, does it? It would be sufficient to make everyone *believe* you have a weapon that can level cities.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “A lie that is not exposed… is the truth.” She stares out the window.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Yes, yes, you understand perfectly well! Better than any other of these chumps I've run into, at least. People fear an image, that's why horror movies are so popular! The monster can't actually jump out of the screen, but the fear is real! To make people crumple in fear without even having to lay a hand on them, and if I have to play some underhanded tricks to reach there, it's all the better!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
She nods.
“Yes. I am the same, in a certain respect. I am up before dawn for the purpose of plotting tricks. You met Skelt earlier, right? He’s obsessed with me. All because I’ve shown this city someone to be adored. I can have any amount of love I want! With my powers, the existence of Neko is in my full control! This is real magic. None of that fireball bullshit.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Hold on, you put all of that work in for the sake of... love and adoration? What the hell is the point of that? What a waste of time! Anyone can be loved, just be one of those pathetic 'good people' or whatever."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She scoffs. “Certainly. Being ‘liked’ is trivial; a default state, even. And being “loved” simply requires putting in the effort. But then what? How do you maintain it? What if your target perishes? I am not so fragile. My reputation is fostered within a hive! I will never die.” She mutters offhandedly. “Well, okay. It’s not a population that can reproduce. But I’ll think of something.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((Voreverl Leocot has met the greatest character in The Antarctica Project.))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Okay, great, good for you. Maybe you are the best at doing what everyone else is already doing, but... so what? Why do you give a shit? *I'm* unique, I'm different from the rest of society! Voreverl Leocot is a menace! Being especially loved is just... It's like being the tallest person in a room. Sure, you're better at it, but who cares, everyone else already has height."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “I wouldn’t expect you to understand. It’s fine. Anyway, I was going to ask, but I was distracted. What’s up with this group? You’re through with Wressy? That creates a minor issue for me.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "This bucket of bolts was the only useful minion there. Wress was easy to manipulate, but utterly spineless when it comes to evil. His plan would be helpful, but I don't *need* society overturned to be feared."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
“Hm. No, this could work. It may even be for the best. Furn, I assume you’ll go along with whatever she wants?”

Furn slowly nods. “…More or less.”

“That splits some of the base devoted to Wress… it was concerning the amount of sway he held. Okay. It’s not a nuke, but I can provide you with a powerful weapon. What I request in return is confidentiality.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, you're making a deal with me? Honesty isn't a trait suited for villains, but I will say that you've given me no reason to trust you... which is all the more reason I have to accept your deal! Whatever betrayal you're planning, I'll outshine it tenfold!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Interesting. Have you heard this riddle, Voreverl? You need to determine some information: which door leads to an escape, what the password is, it doesn’t matter. And your only way of getting information is from two guards. One who always tells the truth. One who always lies. Can it be done?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “Sorry, there’s a friend of mine obsessed with these sorts of things. It came to mind.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl is deep in thought for a moment "Ah... I get it! It's a trick question! Neither tells the truth, there's a third one hidden from view! Quite the betrayal of expectations there, setting up an impossible riddle with a solution so close within reach."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She exhales loudly. “Yeah. Good answer.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl looks proud of herself "If that's the best you can challenge me with, then you're really not a worthy mental opponent. You should just go ahead and pledge your loyalty if you know what's best."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Perhaps. We will see what the future holds.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "So was there any point to that riddle? I'm not seeing any weapon being handed over, and this conversation is starting to get kind of boring. Goody two shoes like you only have so much to offer a force of malice like me."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “I don’t have it. Count that as deceit if you will. I only meant that I know how you can obtain it. I could send you off now with directions, though you’d miss quite the show if you left so early.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...What kind of show? You'll have to make it a good sell for me to bother. I've wasted a lot of my life not reaching the potential terror I could instill in the populace, so I'd prefer to succeed on this side as fast as possible."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “…You’ll see. I want you to play a game.” She smiles enigmatically. ((THE session ends))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: She jolts to attention. "...I need you to go upstairs. Now."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((sending the beginning message minutes earlier im CRAZY))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl tilts her head "Kind of a sudden shift there. What, you got some kind of trap laid for me there? Gweheheh, like you'd have the guts to challenge me so directly."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "They're coming. Horatius and co. You'd like to avoid that, yes? You'll be spotted if you just waltz out into the open."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gwuh- huh!?" Voreverl turns to Furn "I thought you said... Ugh! When am I going to get competent minions!?" Voreverl runs up stairs while yelling "For note, I'm doing this to delay our epic showdown! I could destroy them now easily if I wanted!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
This happens.

The third floor has four podiums in it, as well as some miscellaneous stuff lying around.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well that's quite the odd décor. This is why only villains should be allowed to design lairs." Voreverl inspects the podiums, is there anything special about them.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: ((roll investigation))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
They just seem like podiums to stand at.

Voreverl is messaged on the PDA. ((one sec))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: #unknown-voreverl

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
((Soooorrry we had to wait for someone))

Catarina EVENTUALLY storms up the stairs. "Sorry Voreverl. Change of plans."

((Roll constitution))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Voreverl is electrocuted unconscious.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Good for her.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: No one is in the second floor. Or the first, if you continue.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl leaves the tower in silence.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: This occurs. A voice eventually sounds from behind her. “So what happened, then?” Furn.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl's voice is strained "...I don't want to talk about it. Let's just... find somewhere to stay, or something."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “…Okay. There’s a cheap inn. They also only charge you in the morning, if you’d like to skip the paying.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...That would be a pretty evil thing to do, yeah. Sounds good."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
“Okay.”

They successfully rent a room at the inn.

“There’s a chance the weird white thing tries to approach us again. Do you want me to let it follow us around, or spook it off?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well... it was traveling with that asshole... but you used to be with Horatius, so... I don't know, just use your best judgement." Voreverl lays down in a bed and buries her face in the pillow.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Okay. G…Bad night, or something.” The ambient hum of Furn being active dies down.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((you also finish chapter 5 i forgot to mention because this involves no body loss for you))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl wakes up with Furn carrying her over his shoulder and running.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gwehuh...? Oh, are we avoiding payment...? Good, yeah, nice work. Voreverl Leocot is perfectly capable of running on my own, though." Voreverl has no enthusiasm in her voice.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Yeah, they're a lot smarter than I gave them credit for." Furn ducks into an alleyway to put you down, then keeps running. "We might have lost them by now, but it would probably be the safest option to get out of town."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl follows Furn "...Yeah, that's fine. This place makes me sick, anyway."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
The two of you reach the outskirts of town, at which point Furn again hides in an alleyway to catch his breath which he doesn't have and let you do so.

"We've lost them by now. I assume."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Great... That, uh, shows them for challenging me..." Voreverl begins idly fiddling with her items "...So, about how long did it take for Bern to come back last time? Are we... getting close?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Furn makes an exhaust vent noise. "I don't know. I don't even think it was a full day last time."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Oh, I see... Hey, uh, Furn. You haven't... heard anything about me recently, right?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"No. I--"

Furn is interrupted as a woman turns the corner into this alleyway. He enters a defensive stance.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Hello. Sorry to interrupt. Is there a 'Voreverl Leocot' here?"

author.name: scipe

Are you a fan, or perhaps, do you wish to challenge the dark overlord of evil to end my reign!? A foolish endeavor for a foolish woman!"

messages.content: "Hmm. I suppose a fan would be the best answer. I'm Katrielle. I watched the... well, whatever exactly you'd call it. From yesterday."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-F698C.png

messages.content: "We can skip the weird name hang-ups. I don't really give a damn about that. You're Voreverl Leocot to me. That's enough."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-0650A.png

messages.content: Voreverl clenches her fists "...That's... Of course I am... What else would I be!? Are you just here to spout gibberish or do you actually want something!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "There's no need to be so uptight. I just thought you'd be more comfortable if I dismissed it from the get-go rather than leaving things unsaid. I want to help you."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-B2B87.png

messages.content: "Oh, that's... Gweheheh! Of course you do! Pledging loyalty as a minion of Voreverl Leocot is the only logical choice for any creature with half a brain!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "I... yeah. Sure."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-B0EEB.png

messages.content: "..." Voreverl looks around for a moment "So, uh, new minion! What do you think you can provide someone advanced as Voreverl Leocot!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Transport, for one thing. You're not going to get any conquest done on foot."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-BD227.png

messages.content: "That's... true." Voreverl sighs "So, what, you can teleport us or something?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Ultimately, yes. With my assistance, you'll be able to be anywhere at your convenience."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-59FBE.png

messages.content: "I don't suppose 'anywhere' would include Earth?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Not that I'm aware of. I didn't really get that part of the show."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-C6E66.png

messages.content: "I didn't want to lead with it while I was still just a suspicious intruder, but it's not really something worth hiding. You know Intuition Overdrive, right? From that whole spectacle?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-F7A9F.png

messages.content: Voreverl looks notably annoyed "Ugh, that utter incompetent failure isn't even worth discussing! The fact that I haven't already forgotten about him is my one weakness as an evil ruler! Why are you bringing him up!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Heh. I've never seen anyone get such a thorough and complete read on him in so little time. Well done. I just meant that I can maneuver my way into accessing more or less all of his obscenely versatile connections to organized crime."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-380DA.png

messages.content: "Because he's my son, I mean."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-490DA.png

messages.content: "...Oh." Voreverl turns around and begins to walk away "Furn, we're leaving."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Okay." Furn follows.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I see. How unfortunate. How about this, then?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-7C0E7.png

messages.content: "Accept my help or I'll get you sent to jail."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-D87F5.png

messages.content: "Yeah, sure, whatever. Bern can deal with that when he gets back." Voreverl keeps walking.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "No, he will not." Furn stops.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I could take or leave the tin man, really. That's not very important. But I guess I should've thought that through. You wouldn't really care about going to jail here, right?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-C3DF6.png

messages.content: "You'll be gone from this world later the same way he is now. So I just need to be able to ruin you there too, right?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-910C6.png

messages.content: Voreverl stops, and after a moment, turns around and begins angrily shouting "Ruin me!? Yeah, good luck making my life any worse than it is now! I just... I just wanted people to know my name, to fear my face, to crumple in panic at the very mention of Voreverl Leocot! And now... It's all ruined! It's all fucking ruined! If I couldn't even be Voreverl Leocot here... A place where my past literally doesn't exist, then I don't have a *chance* on Earth! So yeah, go ahead, do whatever you want! I! Don't! Care!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "And what the hell makes you think that's impossible here? Are you giving up, pussy?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-EFC02.png

messages.content: "I was excited to find someone both motivated and competent, but I'll be quite disheartened if both are wrong."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-0F7B6.png

messages.content: "You... You know exactly why it's impossible! Who the fuck fears someone named Jane! Who could ever treat me like a villain when I have such an embarrassing history! I can't *be* Voreverl Leocot anymore! Everyone knows it's... it's not... I'm not..." Voreverl is tearing up now "Just go away! All of you! Stop pretending like you can see me as Voreverl!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Aiding you is merely a courtesy. I am obviously not going to leave." Furn.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Mm. Quite the fix you've found yourself in. I can't afford to quit either, unfortunately. This is my last resort. If I can't succeed now, I'll die as nothing."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-5042B.png

messages.content: "Why did you answer yes when I asked if you knew Intuition Overdrive?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-75E1F.png

messages.content: "Are you an idiot!? You saw me on that farce of a game show! What, do you think I could've lied about that!? 'Oh, no, that was my identical twin Vorgutersloh Aquariuspoly', something like that!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “No, that’s not what I was insinuating. Though that would be pretty funny.” https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/963158984913735742/1021151361947160676/unknown.png

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

thumbnail.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-8F6F1.png

messages.content: “I’m asking why you believe there was anyone of that description with you on that occasion.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-DD053.png

messages.content: "Wh... Because... There was??? You can't gaslight me! Is this your new strategy to convincing me to join you!? Get me to doubt my sanity!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Groverfield. One of the questions was about a family with that name, and Intuition answered under the premise that it was his family. So ‘Intuition Overdrive’ wouldn’t be the name he was born with, right?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-22C98.png

messages.content: “I also wouldn’t have personally chose to name a kid Intuition, but that’s neither here nor there.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-12C5E.png

messages.content: ((I would name a kid Intuition.))

author.name: zzazz
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\00e5cb55aacbe3824e8b8a9d53aac811-1CCD0.png

messages.content: "...Okay, so what? You're telling me that he's not actually Intuition Overdrive? He's John Groverfield or whatever? Great, real helpful! I'm so happy to know I wasn't the only poser there!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “No, I don’t give a damn about that. I’m saying you didn’t pick up on it. It’s not quite as bombastic and obnoxiously delivered, but it was still a whole question in the broadcast.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-30884.png

messages.content: “And that’s for Intuition Overdrive, who’s kind of notorious. You don’t even have that. Your worries contradict each other.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-10117.png

messages.content: “You’re absolutely right. Nobody knows Voreverl Leocot. Nobody fears her or gives a shit about her at this point. I only remembered your name and searched for you for my own potential benefit. So why would they keep track of trivia about this absolute nobody?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-CA743.png

messages.content: “You don’t have nearly that high staying power. When you’ve just implied you want to do things rather than actually doing anything, I guarantee none of the attention deficit morons that suck up to Neko have any awareness of you.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-7BF75.png

messages.content: "..." Voreverl punches the wall of the alleyway "Gweh... Gwehah... GWEHAHAHAH! You're right! You're absolutely right! If Voreverl Leocot isn't a household name, then neither is... is... that other person! I'm still at square zero! This is my villain origin story! That idiotic buffoon of a woman will regret ever even trying to claim that I would ever not be Voreverl Leocot! First I'll rise to infamy, and then enact my revenge on her! And when the history books tell tales of the bloodshed, it shall be Voreverl Leocot that they say commanded the army of evil!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Well said."

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-829EB.png

messages.content: "Okay." Furn.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl raises her fist in the air "Alright! Voreverl Leocot is back on track! No, that's not it, I actually never left! So then, what do you need me for? You've proven yourself incredibly intelligent for managing to reason that out before even I could, so I'll hear out your plans."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "We need to get the hell out of here. For both me and you, doing something attention grabbing in this area would be a bad idea. My son's waste of federal effort is the best option for exiting this corner of Arctica quickly."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-F46FC.png

messages.content: "Ugh, relying on that buffoon doesn't sound very glamorous for a villainous plan... But, I suppose it's not *my* plan." Voreverl shrugs "Alright, let's get out of this frigid wasteland."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "I have no desire to defend my son against this sort of slander. ...I care for him, obviously, in my own way, but he really is an idiot. I only want to clarify that the resources he has inherited access to are no joke. This will work."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-E0DF5.png

messages.content: "Isn't that always how it is... First senile old men like Joe Biden get presidency and laser swords, and now a fool like Intuition gets power in Arctica. Gweheheh, I guess I should be thankful. The underdog villains always come out on top!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Shall we be off, then? It's best if we don't linger."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-F7152.png

messages.content: "Of course, a true villain must be omnipresent, I can't afford to lose time being shackled to this primitive town!" Voreverl sets off in a direction without asking what way they're going.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Furn follows silently, having been usurped as the most important NPC in this scene.

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No idea how you knew it was this way, but alright."
