users.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\00e5cb55aacbe3824e8b8a9d53aac811-1CCD0.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, so, what's the plan here? We break in and steal what we need? Or we swindle it out of them through deceit and betrayal?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "No, none of that. We just... hmph." She stops short after entering the building.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-2C5C2.png

messages.content: "Just... what? Listen, I'm all for keeping plans close to your chest, much easier for betrayal, but if you want to be part of my organization, I'm gonna need you to spit it out."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "No, it's... nothing. The woman at the desk just isn't the same one I knew. That shouldn't be a problem." She walks ahead to talk to this mafiosa.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-3B2B1.png

messages.content: Voreverl follows "Gweheheh! Greetings, fellow villain! I, Voreverl Leocot, have come with my new minion to make use of your services for my evil schemes!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Uh, yeah, anyway. There should be teleportation available from here, right?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-C03E5.png

messages.content: The receptionist(?) stares. "Who the hell are you."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I'm Katrielle Groverfield...? And this is, um... well, you heard her. We're together."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-462EE.png

messages.content: "Never heard of you." The receptionist shoos the two of you away.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
Katrielle turns to you.

"You're like... an adult, right? It's hard to tell for sure at my age. Just want to be sure I don't need to pull any punches. You seem pretty gung-ho about all this."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-0526A.png

messages.content: "...Huh, I never really though to ask how old this body is. Whatever, it doesn't matter, I'm an adult back on Earth, so no matter what appearance, I carry the same maturity and wisdom of age!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Okay, that's good."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-A4C84.png

messages.content: Katrielle stabs the receptionist in the pinky with a pocket knife. She screams.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Does the name feel familiar enough now? Please, let me talk to your superior so I can stop there."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-654A2.png

messages.content: Voreverl takes a step back "Wh... Whoa... That... Gweheh! Heh! Uh, good work, minion! No one denies Voreverl Leocot access and gets away with it intact!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: The receptionist barely makes out some sentence fragments between screaming. "He... gaagh! Not here... communication with... it's down."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Really? What an irresponsible man. Whoever he is. Hey, don't just pull that out, dummy, get a compress first."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-4D2E8.png

messages.content: "So, what, we have to go track down this guy now? Ugh, it's the schemes that are meant to be complicated! Not just getting from one place to another."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
The receptionist tends to her wound, but does not budge in refusing you access.

"I don't think this nobody knows a thing about how teleportation works. But really, the boss MIA...? And I couldn't get a hold of Intuition either. Whatever. We can either break through this place by force, or I could try a different, less reliable way of getting where we need to go. It's a matter of priorities. Physical vs. Metaphysical danger."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-96754.png

messages.content: "Ah... Uh, well..." Voreverl thinks for a moment "As obviously powerful as I am in a fight, as any true villain should be, I'd rather save my debut performance of my skillful battle prowess for a more important, climactic event! What's this other method?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: ((wow i am SO good at juggling responsibilities))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "There's a location I should still be capable of bringing us to, a little more out of the way. I'm a little rusty, but it'll be fine. Probably."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-5762F.png

messages.content: "You've proven yourself capable as a minion, I'll place my trust in you. That is, until I find reason for betrayal, of course. Besides, what's a villain origin story without a little risk!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Katrielle focuses. And a crashing noise is heard. Some kind of teleportation happened, at least.

Voreverl finds herself staring up at an unfamiliar ceiling.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweh? That was quick!" Voreverl shoots up and looks around.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: This looks like the room of a young girl.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...What. Ugh, she must have misunderstood. Children's rooms are *creepy*, not *villainous*. Big difference!" Voreverl tries to leave the room.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: The room is not locked. She exits into a hallway full of doors like the one she just exited. This place appears to be in disrepair.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl groans "How the hell are we supposed to intimidate the heroes if our villainous lair is in such poor condition!? There better be some reason for stopping here, or else I'll need to think of a sufficient punishment for that minion." Voreverl begins looking through the rooms.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Her search is interrupted by Katrielle.

"Sorry about that. Are you alright?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-14B34.png

messages.content: "Gweheh, of course I'm fine! Voreverl Leocot has survived far more dangerous situations! Anyway, what exactly... *is* this place? Certainly not the most pristine location for evildoing."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "It's a whole thing. Have you heard of Pierce's Academy for Women?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-2E8E3.png

messages.content: "Uhhh, no? I've only been in this dimension for like, a couple days. But look, if you're about to go into a big rant about this place, save it. All I need to know is if there's any reason we had to stop at such a dingy place."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "That wasn't my intention, no. It's a dump of a building and it's shut down now. The end. It happens to be a place I could bring us to."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-9C701.png

messages.content: "In that case, let's find my other minion, and get the hell out of here. As they say, time is money, which they also say is the root of all evil, and thus wasting time would be wasting evil!" Voreverl looks around the building for Furn.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Oh. I almost forgot about him. He should be somewhere around." She also searches.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-26176.png

messages.content: ((ok yeah this is voreverl session end lol sucks to suck))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: The two find Furn in a larger dining hall looking area. He's just sort of standing there.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl points to him "Planning to enjoy a feast behind your leader's back, were you, minion? Gweheheh, an excellent betrayal, but you should've known that I would find you."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "What exactly... is this place?" Furn looks all around.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "If you wanted to know, you shouldn't have gone off on your own. All you need to know is that it's not even close to the quality I'd need for an evil lair, so we're leaving."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Yeah. This is just an unfortunate necessary tangent. We were just leaving, golem." She starts walking.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-A4771.png

messages.content: "It feels... unusual being here. I think Bern was once somewhere similar..." Furn trails behind with a noticeably more awkward gait than usual.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well, that certainly tracks. A creepy rundown building for a creepy rundown fool. Really, Arcticans should be counting their blessings for getting to suffer under my wrathful rule rather than deal with him." Voreverl also goes in the direction.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "That's Bernard Zie, right? The Zie family was nobility. Not a surprise that he went to a *school*. Though calling this place a school is something of an inaccuracy."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-134D3.png

messages.content: They reach the front entrance of the building after enough hallway wandering.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Finally. If I wanted to spend more time in school I would've just gone to college. Such restrictive environments are no place for a fully developed mastermind tactician such as myself." Voreverl leaves the building yeah.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "It's not the kind of institution where they teach-- agh, whatever."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-C8B31.png

messages.content: "By the way, are you a boy or a girl? I don't think I really understood that."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-B5696.png

messages.content: Voreverl cringes slightly at the question "Are you an idiot? Look at my mannerisms of a villainess! What kind of man would take on the name Voreverl Leocot!? My body here may be unsuited for displaying my true form, but where I come from, I'm a girl through and through!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "That would've been my guess. Just, something about your knowledge, the way of looking at things..." She shakes her head. "Eh. I know now, and that's that. Is there anywhere specific you need to go, or are we free to follow my lead?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-A4224.png

messages.content: Voreverl thinks for a moment "...Ah! That's right!" she takes out her PDA and glances through the #unknown-voreverl channel again "The city of Sunnyside. I received a tip from a fan. There's something there I should steal, apparently. Gweheheh, my rise to power story has been missing a good heist."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She shrugs. "Sure. Sounds good to me. Could use a trip there, actually."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-28579.png

messages.content: Katrielle pulls out a fucking iPhone. "Gonna try making a call again. Don't mind me."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-F5924.png

messages.content: "So phones exist here... Then why did I get stuck with this primitive toy!?" Voreverl angrily puts away her PDA.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Furn motions you to talk to him as Katrielle begins an extended conversation you can choose if you want to eavesdrop or not.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl chooses to prioritize scheming over the evil act of invading privacy. She moves towards Furn "What is it, minion? Lost without your leader's guidance?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Do you trust this woman?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Minion, 'trust' has no place in the world of villains, and she clearly has some talent in this field. I'm sure she plans to betray us when the time is right, I'd expect no less. But we shall betray her first! At the first opportunity to get one over on her, we'll take what we can and win this silent battle of wits!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "...Do you think she trusts you?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Being trusted is the most insulting thing that could happen to a villain! I've made it clear who I am: an indomitable force of evil. Anyone with half a brain wouldn't trust me."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Okay." Furn stops talking for a few full seconds. "So if you think she is going to stop working in your interest eventually... and she thinks the same of you... is anyone actually getting betrayed?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: The group is WALKING through all of this wow

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well, that's..." after a few moments of silence, Voreverl grabs her head "Ugh! Shut up! I should've known it would be pointless to expect a mere minion to understand the intricacies of my evil! It's... uh... it's a double bluff! It's so *obvious* that I'm going to betray her, that she probably expects I won't betray her as a betrayal of her expectations! And then I'll betray her anyway!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Okay, jeez." Furn turns away. "You're all so fragile. Bern's the same way, rambling self-contradictally when he's pushed on a certain topic. I don't understand it. I'm supposed to have the same sort of soul as any of you. So why don't I end up subject to these fits of hysteria? I guess being made of metal helps."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Katrielle is done her call, also.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I'll tell you why, it's because you're a common minion! You don't *need* to be offended, because no one will think lower of you than what you are. I'm a grand villain! If people don't respect that... then they're just fools! That's all there is to it!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Hmph." Furn does not respond further.

They reach the fucking town of Sunnyside and also specifically the building specified in #unknown-voreverl

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That fan of mine lacked the ability to properly explain what exactly I'm meant to steal from here, so keep your eyes out for anything properly villainous. Got it, minions?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Furn grunts.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I'll let you know if anything is suspicious."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-9D203.png

messages.content: "Very good... or rather, very evil!" Voreverl checks if the building is unlocked.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: It is.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl barges into the building and looks around.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: There is a young woman and two children who look to be about like less than ten years old.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Hey, Voreverl, I see someone."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-49888.png

messages.content: "Who... are you?" The young woman asks.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, who am I? Voreverl Leocot is disappointed at your ignorance, but thanks you for giving me the opportunity for another proper introduction! I am the conqueror of worlds, I am the blight upon this land, I am the end of everything you hold dear! Evil mastermind Voreverl Leocot will now be raiding your house!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
One of the children, a boy, laughs. "You're fun. I like her, Theresa." He turns to the adult, who buries her face in her hands.

"I'm not interested in buying anything. I make a meager living, and I have just enough to support myself. And I guess these two, for the imminent future."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Gweh? You misunderstand, I'm not offering, I'm taking. Keep your money, foolish commoner. I'll be searching your house and seizing whatever it is I came here for. You don't need to play any part in this scheme."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"What? Kids, go play outside."

"But--" the boy objects.

"I'm not fuckin' asking." She glares at this tiny child, causing him and his sister to abscond. Then turns back to Voreverl.

"What do you want?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl's eyes follow the children as they leave, before returning to the woman "Well, I wouldn't expect any old fool like you to understand, but a villain like me needs power to intimidate her subjects. I was told there was something I'd want to steal from here, to help my evil scheme come to fruition!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She sighs. "Dagte collected a lot of weird shit. You can check his room, I guess?" She points to a door in the house.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, you see that, minions? Voreverl Leocot has successfully interrogated the information out of her! Even without my full potential, my intimidation is unparalleled." Voreverl goes to the room.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: The room contains a weird floating light. This is the most imminently obvious thing about it. It also has copious amounts of canned fish, books, and pieces of paper.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I see his game. He must have known I was coming and placed these canned fish as a diversion. Unfortunately for him, he got me mixed up with Voreverl Jr.! As a human, I see through his deceit! This challenge is nothing for Voreverl Leocot!" Voreverl goes up to the light and tries to grab it.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Voreverl's body like. Kinda absorbs it?

And then she blacks out. ((chapter finish))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: You awaken in a car. Eric Zeety is in the driver's seat.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: You're sitting in the front passenger side.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl takes a moment to process this, staring at Eric, and then fist pumps in the air "Yes! Gwehahahah! I'm back! That's why a villain always trusts her fans! Goodbye fake world, hello future domain of Voreverl Leocot!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Eric turns to you in shock. "Voreverl?!"

You hear the voice of Meryl Leiblich. "THE ROAD, ERIC! EYES ON THE ROAD!"

Eric narrowly avoids a car accident, and then pulls over to a side street. 

"Is it... really you?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What, you get convinced that idiotic parasite would stay in here forever? Gweheheh, maybe that would save the world from my tyranny, but I won't allow it to happen! Earth's citizens will weep upon hearing my return!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "That's... good." Eric looks over at the back seat, and then back at you. "Voreverl... do you know what today is?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Trying to quiz your leader? Very well, I'll allow a demonstration of my brilliant deductive reasoning as an evil mastermind. I slept overnight in Arctica, which means that today is [the day after the day it was the last time she was on Earth]! Really, it's basic addition, far below my skill level."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "I see. I was worried about that." Eric sighs. "Voreverl, it's October 6. I haven't seen you in four months. Well, not 'you' you."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl takes a moment before responding, very taken off guard "...Nice... betrayal! You've learned well, making up such a ridiculous lie like that to trap me! Or is this a test of my observations? A good villain needs to be able to read her opponents!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "I don't need to get into an argument about this. You can figure things out on your own, just... I'm here to help, if you want." Eric starts driving again. "You want me to drop you off at your place?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "..." Voreverl checks what items she has on her.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: PDA, phone, keys. The wallpaper of the phone has been changed to "VOREVERL CHECK NOTES APP".

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl checks the date on the phone.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: October 6.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It's really... Then what... Where have I... Where have I been!? I was only in Arctica for a day! Where... What happened to me!?" Voreverl grabs her hair and begins pulling at it in frustration.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Eric frowns. "I don't know. I swear, I've tried to fix things this whole time, but it's just... an enigma."

"Is that... her now, then? Actually?" Meryl.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Yes! Of course it's me! Ugh! Why wouldn't... No, no! That idiot! Why couldn't he just get out of my body! Voreverl Leocot! That's me! This is Voreverl Leocot's body!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Oh. Yes. That's good, then." Meryl.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "So... So what the hell has Bern been doing with my body!? Do I still work... Am I still using the zoo as a cover!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Yeah, he took a few days off early on, but realized it was best for both of you if that stayed consistent. Grumbled about it constantly, though. He's not much of an animal lover, clearly." Eric rolls his eyes.

He looks back briefly. "Uh, nothing else really of note with your body. I've done everything I can to stop Bern from violating your privacy, and he's been pretty reasonable about it. You'll have no trouble using him if the need arises, I'm sure." He coughs. "By the way, do you know this guy?" 

Eric points to the unconscious body of Horatius Kyodu sprawled across the furthest back seat of the car behind where Meryl is sitting.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...What... What the fuck are they doing here!?" Voreverl instinctively moves her body as far from Horatius as possible "Dump them! Throw them in jail! Trap them in a room filling with piranha infested water! I don't even care how they got here, just... Get rid of them!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Okay. I’ll deal with it.” Eric stares ahead with a neutral expression.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Why won't they just stay out of my life!? Ugh! Can anything go right!? This is humiliating for a villain! I've wasted so much time... No, no! I haven't wasted it, I've just... Voreverl Leocot didn't exist! Four months without her! It's not fair!" Voreverl buries her face in her hands.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
“Dear, y-“ Meryl starts speaking in a concerned tone and is interrupted.

“Miss Leiblich. You claim to love her, right? Then leave. You’re not what she needs.” Eric parks the car. Meryl stands there silently in shock.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Gweh... heheh! Indeed! A classic betrayal! Throw out this, uh, this old-fashioned..." Voreverl doesn't finish this thought.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
Meryl shuffles out silently.

Eric sighs. “It’s a bunch of bullshit is what it is.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "E-exactly! But... But this is just setting the stage! Powerscaling my brilliance! The harder the circumstances, the more brilliantly the villain shines when she stomps on everything the heroes hold dear! That's all this is... yeah! A test!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “I hope. I myself have run out of ideas by this point. Avdol’s utterly useless, and the Pope hasn’t said anything for some time.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Don't worry, I'll think of something! I'll defeat those fools! I don't need anyone else! Religion is a joke! I never expected that idiot at the top to be of use!" while saying this, Voreverl looks back to her phone and opens the notes app.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
> Voreverl Leocot - 
> 
> I know how to use the phone now. I don't plan on doing it much beyond this and basic communication, though. I guess I'll put down what I had written to you when I thought this was going to be the same as the first time, with information added from the time since then. Maybe this is just for me? I don't know if I'll ever get back. I'm going to keep assuming I will.
> 
> I don't accept you as my boss, obviously. I've never backed down against an opposing force! But I also don't really care about opposing your aims. It seems obvious that Earth is subject to certain problems. It's closer to ideal than Arctica, but there are those who subvert the way it ought to be.
> 
> Your Pope is a blasphemer and a windbag, while the politicians in the rest of Italy are mediocre. Avdol is insufferable, and seems particularly dismissive of women. The United States, the former most powerful region, is in chaos due to executive failure. Everyone we can find who opposes The Antarctica Project seems especially awful, which makes things difficult.
> 
> The more personal connections you have are much more tolerable. Eric is a very funny guy who I am amazed still sticks by you(/me). The boss lady is fine. Your mother is overly sentimental. While it lends itself well to conversation as a peer, Id guess the lack of proper discipline from her combined with your clearly absent other parent is what led to you becoming so unhinged. I may have hated dodging blows from my father, but it let me develop a sense of what was and wasn't acceptable. You've been freed to run amok. I can only imagine what you've done in my shoes for all this time.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
> I suppose that's not my business. You have your life, and I have mine, and we're stuck with this. Eric will fill you in on most things if you come back, I assume, with the EDF or whatever. But he seems unusually touchy about Horatius, so I'll mention here that someone who I know from Arctica showed up on [date like two months ago] before passing out and never arising. Their name is Horatius Kyodu, and they are caught up in something similar to us. I dunno the big implications of this, but I suppose we aren't the only two transferring between worlds.
> 
> You're an unusual lady. Good luck.
> 
> - Your enemy and housemate, Bernard Zie

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((Eric IS a funny guy so true))

author.name: legoskelton
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\7324d6b2e5e7b2d85c445c799b852d80-F5E1E.png

messages.content: Voreverl deletes the note after reading it "Pretentious jackass, what the hell does he know. It's shocking he had the brains to realize his perfect society is just a junkyard." She turns her phone off and glances back at Horatius "Gweheheh, so, they braindead or something? Serves them right! That's what you get for messing with Voreverl Leocot!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Something like that. I don't know. Maybe that's what would've happened to your body these past four months if Bern wasn't switching with you. It's creepy as hell, y'know."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Well, I suppose he has his place as a minion. His attitude could use a lot of work, though. Whatever, who cares about those fools. What exactly was going on when I got here? Why were you driving around m-... Meryl?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "She happened upon Bern and they got along reasonably well. Tried to trick her into thinking it was her daughter but she figured things out eventually. She's mainly useful for her connections. Meryl has a long history of involvement with the groups that oppose The Antarctica Project."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "He... That disgusting... Ugh! To think this body could ever be associated with being her daughter again! He should be glad I'm a merciful villain. Whatever, whatever! Are we any closer to taking down The Antarctica Project or not? That's all that matters! I need to use it for my rise to villainy!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Your mom's kinda irrelevant, unfortunately. All the associates she knew of are too busy with their own political woes. They should be available if we need something specific, but they're unwilling to act. Whoever he is, whatever he wants, John Leiblich is closer to the truth than we are right now. So I think our next step is to catch up with him."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That woman is not my mother. But yes, yes, that makes sense. Those filler 'villains' in the seats of government are as inept as they are irrelevant! We shall act ourselves, and lay a trap to capture that fool who thinks himself a master schemer in this stepping stone for the first page of my villainous legacy! So, uh, do we have any leads on where to find him?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "I don't think he's left the US. Some of Meryl's remaining connections have heard from him, but they're tight-lipped. He's supposedly plotting to seize political power, now that -- oh, yeah, uh, Joe Biden is gone now, that's a whole thing. His VP has taken power, but there's a lot of uncertainty over in the states."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: legoskelton
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\7324d6b2e5e7b2d85c445c799b852d80-F5E1E.png

messages.content: "Yeah, yeah, I know. I saw Joe in Arctica. Asshole tried to kill me! Obviously didn't get a scratch on me, but it was still treason against Voreverl Leocot, dark overlord of evil!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Bizarre." Eric shakes his head. "Look, ah... I'll deal with arranging a way for us to confront John." 
He's quiet for a bit.
"What exactly do you think of Bern? I know you certainly aren't happy with what's happening, and you've only seen him through indirect bits of information, but just... I'm curious."

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Uh, let's see. He's a creep, he's a parasite, he's an idiot with braindead ideals, and he has laughably bad fashion sense. His cooperation is the only good quality I've heard, to be frank."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Yeah, I-- creep, huh? I get most of that. But, it's kind of, I mean there's an appeal to that. The idealism. It's stupid, but, that's the sort of thing. Because everyone's kind of dumb, when you get down to it. That's like, it's sort of how I acted when I was a kid. The hero of justice nonsense. It's basically roleplay, but they really believe in it. So seeing it in someone else, it's like. They're able to have happiness I can't. And I don't -- I mean I'm not happy every time someone else is happy, but when it's so close to how you once were, it's sort of, it would be an affront to your own..."

Eric is silent for a few seconds, save for his breathing.

"Well, anyway, I think he's probably gay. Hasn't acted on that, but it's probably true. Thought you should know."

He parks, having arrived at Voreverl's place.

messages.content: "Gweheheh, so he chooses to be a homosexual against society's standards... Quite the evil act." Voreverl gets out of the car, but turns back to Eric "I have no interest in the childish 'roleplay' of a fake hero like him. It's just embarrassing, plain as that. You better drop that sentimentality if you hope to survive in my evil empire!" She closes the car door and walks to her apartment.

messages.content: "Gweh? Don't these fools know when to leave a mastermind alone. I need time for planning!" Voreverl grumpily walks over to her door and looks through the peephole to check who it is.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

author.name: scipe

messages.content: Voreverl takes a step back from the door, and then, without opening it, yells towards it "What do you want!? I'm too important to bother with the trifling matters of fools who would get in the way of my work like you! If you wish to challenge me, know that I'd defeat you easily, so there's no point!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
She yells through the door. "I spent fuckin' months locked up because of last time, I'm not gonna do it again! They confiscated anything I could use, anyway!"
She pauses. "This is-- it's in your interest too, maybe. I don't understand you, but surely you must be a little curious."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\unknown-8DC5A.png

messages.content: "Curious? Gwehah! Not likely! What could you, someone who never understood the brilliance of my evil schemes, possibly have to offer me!? I already know everything someone of your intelligence level would, and way more!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Are you fucking joking? You *know everything*??? Okay, then, genius. Let's start with this: why did I go to prison for *months* for a single incident of aggravated assault with no lasting injuries and no witnesses? I certainly don't remember you showing up to press charges!"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well obviously the courts are afraid of what I'd do if they didn't punish you! Society would crumble! The legal system would collapse! All of this, because of me, Voreverl Leocot! And I'll still do it if you don't know your place!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Hmng. You're not that far off from what I imagine is the truth. Comparatively. All of those sentences but one were absolutely incoherent. I mean, you're someone the legal system hates, right? Isn't that your persona? You could at least lie about being someone cool, rather than someone who gets coddled by all of society."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I... No, that's not what I meant! I got here through my raw talent as a villain! Controlling society from the shadows is a classic villain move! You can hardly get more evil than that! And yet I do anyway! Just because those foolish wannabe villains in government hate me, doesn't mean I can't intimidate them into submission!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "I checked with the woman at the zoo, you know. You weren't even conscious by the time I was sentenced."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Well, uh, that's because I planned it all out ahead of time, duh! I manipulated you into getting arrested as revenge! You've been following the script of Voreverl Leocot, master schemer, from the very beginning!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Sure thing, I bet you're enough of a psychopath to actually think that's true. So what's the answer you come up with in this part of your script? Y'know, when I ask you what you think would happen if you didn't have your rich fuckin' daddy to bail you out every time you shit yourself?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl bangs on the door "Voreverl Leocot does not have a father! That... that man is my enemy! He is a fool that I must crush on my progress to absolute evil! Whatever you *think* he did to help me, you're clearly mistaken!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Oh, sure. And that Eric kid, him too? Another person not helping you, another place you have total control?! I could tolerate how shitty of a person you are, you know. It comes with the territory of being a rat bastard rich kid. But this is the sticking point, any time I tried or still try to extend a hesitant arm. It's that you're a fucking moron, Jane. I don't know what she ever saw in you."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "And I don't know what the hell you're talking about! If you're going to insult me, at least be smart enough to get my name right! At least you got one thing right, I *am* a terrible person! I'm the worst person! I exude malevolence by my very presence! So it doesn't surprise me that idiots like you try to make yourselves rivals of mine! Well guess what, it's not gonna happen! I'm way above the level of your childish banter!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: There is no response.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Gweheh... Gweheheheh! Yeah! That's what I thought! No one talks back to Voreverl Leocot!" Voreverl looks through the peephole again to see if she's left.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: She has left.

messages.content: Voreverl moves away from the door "Just as well, I can't be bothered when I have scheming to do! Where to start, though..." Voreverl takes out her PDA and looks through the recent messages.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "So a minion can be brought with me... What a shame that all of my *useful* ones are on the other side. Still, anyone handpicked by my genius mind would surely be better than a random lowlife." Voreverl checks the time that it is right now.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

It’s slightly late. Like 7 or something.

Another knock on your door. “Voreverl?”

Eric (Eric)

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Hey, we should get going, uh…” He checks his phone. “…Now. Or soon. Francis could book us a flight, but apparently not a *convenient* one. I don’t anticipate we’ll need to be there for that long, but you can pack whatever.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You... you've already arranged it? I underestimated you. Perhaps I do have a useful minion on this side as well." Voreverl looks at her PDA "I *was* planning on bringing one of our zoo animals with me, but if we have a flight to catch... Yes, I suppose you'll do." Voreverl holds out the PDA "Take this."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What is this, exactly?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "A communications device. Being the genius mastermind that I am, I was able to get my hands on it, giving me exclusive access to knowledge on The Antarctica Project! Such as how to bring one of my minions with me."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Oh, that's interesting. How's that?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, here's the classic Voreverl betrayal. I've already demonstrated it to you! By holding this device, you've become linked with my transfers! My evil scheme is falling into place!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: ((oh no what will eric do now))

author.name: zzazz

messages.content: "..." Eric stares in confusion, and, perhaps something else, at Voreverl for a few seconds. "I... I see. That's... cool."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: He clears his throat. "Do you... want to go? I don't want to feel like I'm pressuring you with this whole fixation on going where John Leiblich is."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What kind of question is that? He's my current rival. I need to topple his empire in order to rule my own! It's only natural that Voreverl Leocot would come to end his reign!" Voreverl also snatches back the PDA and pockets it.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Okay. Yeah, of course. Wouldn't be the great and terrible Voreverl Leocot if you settled for anything less!" Eric turns away. "I'll go call over a taxi. Pack what you need in the meantime."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Good delegation, minion. I was about to assign us the same roles." Voreverl packs some clothes, toothbrush and toothpaste, and a box of cereal for an evil snack.

messages.content:
((ok yeah we are funny skipping))

The ride to the airport occurs uneventfully. Eric’s quiet. He’s a little more talkative there, though mainly to figure out where the flight is. The two of you finally make it on THE PLANE‼️

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “Do you fly often, Voreverl? I’m assuming you’ve done it at least once before.” Eric.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "An astute observation. I could have swam to Italy on my own, but it was more evil to take up a seat on a plane that someone more innocent could have used. Although, I, uh, haven't been on one for a bit. I decided to trick the government into thinking it could control me by not traveling. Before my arrest, I did it plenty. It lets me look down on the world and see all the nations that will fear me!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Yeah, everything is real small from up here. It’s… something else.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...I do find it a bit sickening, in a way. Everything becomes so... hard to tell apart. Someone looking down from a plane would never know if they were directly above Voreverl Leocot or not! It all just looks the same."

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Yeah. All the more reason to get above it all.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, indeed. Maybe when I conquer the Earth, I'll build myself a flying nation! No one will be able to ignore that sight!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, I'm really back in my home turf. Those fools in the American government won't know what hit them now that I've completed my training as a villain!" Excited to reach their destination, Voreverl pushes her way off the plane as fast as she can.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Eric follows behind, even engaging in one shove himself. “It’s a bit of a walk to the place in question, but we can be pretty confident this is the right place. There’s gonna be *something* there, at least.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Whatever we find, I, Voreverl Leocot, will be able to make use of it to further my evil schemes! We've been too long without progress! But we can't let our enemies feel safe, we must demonstrate how we are encroaching on their territory! Make them fear us!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “It’s true. Let’s burn it down, alright? This whole rotten world.” Eric grins.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Yes! Exactly! Destroy this society and laugh at those fools trying to rebuild it, before crushing their hope again and again! That's what a villain does!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Eric starts walking with a destination in mind. “I’m guessing you, uh, don’t speak regularly with John.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...You could say that. Not that I need to, anyway. There's nothing a weakling sheep like him could teach me! This project is the perfect opportunity to demonstrate that!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: “Good. No holding back. I don’t want us to waste this chance we’ve been given.” The two arrive at a fucking pizzeria.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Are you... sure this is the place? I mean, nothing against pizza, it's a perfectly devious meal to trick people into burning the rooves of their mouth with, but, uh, I was expecting something a bit more..." Voreverl follows this up with some incomprehensible hand gestures.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
“No, this is it. Let’s go.” Eric punches out the nearest person and waves an obviously fake gun in the air.
“EVERYONE ON THE FUCKING GROUND!” He runs past the cowering masses into the back of the building.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweh...? I, uh... Gwehahahah! Yes! Fear us!" Voreverl runs after Eric after taking a moment to shake off her surprise.

messages.content: Voreverl turns her attention towards John, not paying mind to anything else "...So... this whole time... you knew I wasn't me... you knew I wasn't her... and you let me believe anyway!? You couldn't just tell me I had no chance of being who I wanted!? You asshole! Slime! You... you... what the fuck is wrong with you!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
One of the two women who just entered gestures vaguely to the older man still in the cell, confused by but not especially concerned about everything else happening in the room. "Your highness. Recognize anyone?"

"...Huh?" The taller one stares, confused.

John Leiblich shakes his head. "Hmph. You're making a scene here. Yeah, I didn't explain anything to you. So what? Blame your mother. She's the one who pretended to care."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Oh, you think this is a scene!? You haven't seen anything! You want to ruin my plans, my identity!? Fine! But don't expect me to just silently accept it! You can't boss me around, you were never my father! And she was never my mother! It... it would've been better to just die than live like this! What the hell is the point of a life if I can't be Voreverl Leocot!?"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
John doesn't respond.

"...That's Bruce Praxis. Your son. I hope you are able to see the resemblance." The woman turns away more generally to the whole room. "Are any of you John Leiblich?"

"No, that's... Detlef? Why is he here?" The second woman, who I will address as Zita for convenience, mumbles this. ((i love two barely related occurrences))

"I'm John Leiblich!" John Leiblich yells this louder than he needs to.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
"...Okay. Er. John Leiblich. Whoever you are under the impression this is, you must release him. Dreng, too."

"Who the hell are you? I'm incredibly busy." John Leiblich stares at Voreverl, then at the place Klaud exited from.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Oh, are you busy? That's so sad. Poor little pathetic unloved John Leiblich is swarmed with work? What a surprise! Really taking me off my game here, finding out that *John Leiblich* wouldn't have time to properly deal with this! Why don't you cry a river of tears about it so I can drown you in it! Not patricide anymore, you know! Not that it ever was!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
John has an incomprehensible exchange with the interloper about Arctican politics before sighing. "Too many irons in the fire lately."

He looks at his few remaining men. "Take this kid and her friend outside. The grown-ups are talking."

They attempt to drag Voreverl off.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: The Arctican ‼️ stares at Voreverl. "Be quiet, girl. This needs to end as quickly as possible. I'd reiterate the grown-ups are talking, but your father here clearly isn't fully developed either."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Shut up... shut the fuck up! He's not my father, I am an adult, and I will not be leaving! I might not be who I want... but I can at least ruin your life like mine was ruined! You'll face the wrath of... of... me!" Voreverl attempts to break free.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: ((roll for this))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: Voreverl three stooges two generic bodyguards into running into each other, evading capture. Eric isn't as lucky, and gets dragged off.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
"I do not care if you stay here or not. Just shut up. Please." The Arctican ‼️ 
"I could live with that." John halfheartedly mutters.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Gweheheh, you're trying to boss me around? Look lady, I don't know who the hell you are, and I don't care, because there's bigger things on the line here! I wouldn't expect you to understand, but Voreverl Leocot is dead! And I have to take revenge! Whatever you're doing can wait!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content: "She's dead? Thank God. One less person jumping between worlds for me to worry about."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Oh... you're relieved... gweheh... I guess I succeeded at least a bit then... at least one person is responding properly to the death of the villain! That's right! The world is saved! The evil has been exorcised! Now you're just left with me, whoever the fuck I am!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Yeah, whatever." She turns back to John. "This doesn't have to be a big ordeal. Frankly, I have no idea how keeping these two here benefits you at all. Whatever you're hoping to gain, it's stuck in the shadow of something far bigger than yourself, so if you know what's good for you, you'll let them go."

“I need Joe Biden. Only he has the kind of narrative weight that’ll work.” John stares at beloved character Wozniak Dreng. “Uh, I could take or leave this kid? He’s really just here for a lack of anywhere else to be.”

The Praxis in jail has been kind of zoning out for a good five minutes. Wozniak Dreng gets bored of not being in the story and screams at Voreverl. “Why do you even fucking care? You wouldn’t be yelling this much if you didn’t have some complex about his approval.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl turns to Wozniak with a glare "Oh, and why do *you* care about what I want!? Stay out of this! Who even are you!? You want to know why I care!? I care because Voreverl Leocot is more important than any of this shit! I don't care about that roach of a man, he's nothing to me! An ant about to be trampled by my revenge!"

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
"Biden?" The two interlopers speak amongst themselves. "Of course we can hand over Biden, can't we? I can't promise that it will be immediate, but rest assured that he will be in your hands for as long as you need him."

The one I said I’d call Zita trails off in confusion. “I don’t even know who Joe Biden is, really. Is that an earse thing? One of the characters from the anti-arctica project or what-have-you? …Oh my goodness, is that where we are? I just put that together…”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Also Wozniak just goes Tch and returns to sulking alone.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I... said... Voreverl Leocot is more important than any of this! So shut up about your stupid politics!" Voreverl attempts to throw one of the computers in the room to regain everyone's attention.

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png

messages.content:
The Arctican cringes. "...That doesn't- eugh. That doesn't matter. The Antarctica Project doesn't matter. It's not going to exist for much longer anyway. Joe Biden is the name of the culprit in my home-invasion-slash-murder. The old man we have detained. Why- why am I the one to tell you this?"

“I’m sorry. Condolences to the victims, but this seemed kind of superfluous and meaningless. Lower priority that I could let more relevant persons handle. I just — I have a lot to keep track of, Joliene.” ((Im done with the joke im making the channel))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Voreverl has walked into a hallway.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: She keeps walking down this hallway! Angrily!

author.name: natyobb
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\ba6cc976522571d97f7cf7d74d5b3684-FF145.png
